-- French Nuclear Dismantling Might Cost EU22 Bln, Tribune Says
-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 2012-01-12T06:42:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/french-nuclear-dismantling-might-cost-eu22-bln-tribune-says.html
Dismantling  France ’s nuclear plants
might carry a price tag of 22.2 billion euros ($28 billion),  La
Tribune  said, citing a draft report by France’s audit body Cour
des Comptes.  Nuclear dismantling costs pose significant uncertainties,
according to the Cour des Comptes report, La Tribune said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
